====Usage notes====
Noun senses 3 and 4, and verb sense 2, are considered incorrect in some circles; in all probability, the use of ''kick start'' to mean "revitalize" or "provide impetus" was derived from the [[metaphor]]ical use of ''[[jump start]]'' in that sense.

